HEADWORD: Preataxic
<hw>Pre`a*tax"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
<def>Occurring before the symptom ataxia has developed; -- applied to
the early symptoms of locomotor ataxia.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

